# Vendored Exaecut/vekl snapshot.
# NOT committed — the authoritative source lives at github.com/Exaecut/vekl.
# Local devs: run `./scripts/sync-vekl.sh` before `cargo publish` so the
#             published tarball ships with vekl bundled for crates.io users.
# CI: the publish workflow clones vekl fresh on every run.
# Local builds inside the Exaecut workspace don't need this path populated
# because `compile_shaders` falls back to `../vekl` (sibling submodule).
/vekl
